name: FingerPunk #005 (Seguaro Sam)
description: Seguaro Sam isn't actually a finger. He passes as one because he was grown by the most famous Bonsai master in the Hicetnunc metaverse. He is rather annoying to the other FingerPunks since his spines are the cause of many prickly pokes. Splinters are the most common injury a FingerPunk receives.
